Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar korona (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan yanayin a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa duk da cewa matakin ya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da kuma rukunin kula da gaggawa su ƙara kasancewa a shirye don ƙara yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da za su bukaci kulawar lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton wani rukuni na cututtukan huhu na sanadin rashin lafiya a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ruwaito cewa, sabon kwayar cutar korona da ake kira yanzu SARS-CoV-2 ne ke haifar da cutar.
Tun daga lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar kwayar cutar korona (COVID-19).
Shaida ta zuwa yanzu ita ce kusan kashi 80 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, suna da kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi tare da ko ba tare da alamu ba, kuma yawancinsu suna murmurewa.
A kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari, cutar ta COVID-19 ta ƙaru zuwa mummunar cuta da ke bukatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke fama da mummunar cuta da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da suka yi jinya saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yawan COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Ƙasar Ingila (UK) kuma mun gwada su da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma gwada adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ƙasar Ingila
Bayan abin da ya faru a China, COVID-19 ya ƙara yaduwa ta hanyar ƙasa kuma yana bin sahun duniya na COVID-19 a halin yanzu a wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar EuroSurvivals na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an bayar da rahoton mutane uku na farko da aka tabbatar da su daga Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 daga mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan kwanan wata, an ba da rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a dukan duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushe na hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, da hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da kuma WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
A matsayin ma'auni na yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a tsakanin kwanaki 14, sannan kuma mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da adadin adadin waɗanda aka ba da rahoto a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, tare da kwatanta shi da adadin da aka samu a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
An bi yanayin yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin (Hoto na 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya gaba ɗaya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Supplementary material).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin waɗanda aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a yawan COVID-19 (mataki na gaba).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An nuna cewa tun daga 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun bayar da rahoton adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da ya yi daidai da wanda aka samu a Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata ko kuma kasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 na ƙaruwa cikin sauri a Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Ƙasar Ingila.
Yanayin da ake gani a yawan COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa a cikin irin wannan saurin a dukan ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, kuma duk da cewa amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa sun bambanta, ƙayyadaddun yanayi na ƙasashe da ladabi na zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda za a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin biyewa, na iya bambanta.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai zurfi kuma majiyoyin labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da raka'o'in kulawa mai zurfi a wadannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar karfin su.
A halin yanzu akwai bayanai game da asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai zurfi na COVID-19 a duk fadin EU/EEA na kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su a hanya mai tsari domin a ƙara yawan bayanan da ake da su na lura da yawan mutane da suka kamu da cutar da kuma yawan mutuwar da suka faru.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun gado na kulawa mai zurfi da na matsakaici a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye ko ƙasa da na Italiya (kwana 12.5 na kulawa mai tsanani da matsakaicin kulawa ga mutane 100,000 a 2010).
Yanayin samfurin da ya danganci wadatar kulawar lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya don yaduwar COVID-19 da ke haɗarin shiga asibiti sama da &gt; 90% na ƙarfin gado na kulawa mai mahimmanci, ana samun su a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Turai ta COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment.
Tun da yake an tattara cututtuka a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da kuma a Ƙasar Ingila, kuma asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya suna kula da takamaiman yankuna, an fi son a ba da bayani game da cututtuka da kuma gado na kula da marasa lafiya a matakin cibiyar kula da marasa lafiya na yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Ƙasar Ingila.
Saboda haka, dole ne jihohi, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa su shirya kansu don yanayin watsa SARS-CoV-2 na al'umma mai dorewa da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa ta lafiya, musamman kulawa mai zurfi, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
