Binciken hadarin nan da nan ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai iyakantaccen dama da kasashe za su iya ƙarawa wajen sa ido don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan kulawar lafiya.
Idan wannan bai yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da suke bukatar kulawa mai zurfi a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar korona 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ke haifar da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ta kashe mutane fiye da 3,000, kuma ta raunata mutane fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, ta haifar da bala'i na jin kai.
SARS-CoV-2, kamar irin wannan kwayar cutar, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban mutane da cutar SARS a 2003, kuma za a iya yada shi daga batsa kuma ya haifar da irin wannan bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Ko da yake, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan haɗari da mutuwar SARS amma yana da yaduwa da tasiri a tsakanin tsofaffi fiye da matasa da kuma tsakanin maza fiye da mata.
Domin a amsa yawan littattafan da ake wallafawa game da wannan cuta da ke tasowa, wannan talifin yana so ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan bincike da ke ci gaba da sauri.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da annobar cutar, da abubuwan da ke haddasa ta, da ilmin ƙwayoyin cuta, da gane ta, da magani, da kuma yadda za a iya tsinkayar ciwon, da kuma yadda za a iya hana cutar.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar cutar da take barazana da kuma kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa yin irinsa ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka bukaci su zauna a gidajensu a lokacin hutu da makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda sabon barkewar cutar kwayar cuta.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar korona (COVID-19), wadda ta haifar da barkewar cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya mata suna SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma ta sanya wa cutar da ke da nasaba da ita suna COVID-19.
Annobar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa ko'ina a kasar, da kuma kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 80,000, tare da fitar da fiye da marasa lafiya 40,000 daga asibiti da mutuwar fiye da marasa lafiya 3,000.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine babban makiyin jama'a kuma yana iya zama mai ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga fiye da bincike 200 game da COVID-19 wanda ya haɗa da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman, annobar cutar, abubuwan da ke haifar da shi, ganewar asali, da magani, tun lokacin da aka ba da rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya gano jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita na da manufar taƙaita ci gaban bincike a sabon batun da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta da ke haifar da cutar, wato cutar MERS, wanda ya barke a shekara ta 2012.
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka sani game da rigakafin cuta da kuma yadda za a iya yin hasashen cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da har yanzu ake yi.
An yi la'akari da cewa kwayar cutar korona ba ta kashe mutane ba, kuma tana da alhakin kusan kashi 15 cikin 100 na zazzabin sanyi na kowa.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni mun fuskanci kwayar cutar korona biyu da ta yi sanadiyar mummunar cuta ga mutane, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wadanda suka fara bullowa a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, bi da bi, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa da gagarumar yaduwar cuta da kuma mutuwar mutane.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta kwayar cutar corona a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1, an fara bayar da rahoton rukunin cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an sake gano kwayar cutar korona.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, Wuhan ta ba da rahoton mutuwar mutum na farko.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, wanda ke nuna yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan tare da dakatar da dukkan hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ruwaito cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, marasa lafiya 21 ne kawai suka sami hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan, wanda aka ɗauka a matsayin wurin da kamuwa da cuta ta samo asali daga asalin dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin da aka wallafa wannan rahoto, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk fadin kasar Sin da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya (Figure 2.2).
Yayin da lamarin ke ci gaba da hanzari, har yanzu ba a tantance ainihin girman cutar da kuma yadda take da hatsari ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken cibiyoyi da yawa da aka gudanar kan marasa lafiya 8,866 ciki har da marasa lafiya 4,021 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 ya ba da ƙarin bayani game da annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya shafi mutane na dukan shekaru, amma ya fi shafar waɗanda suke tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan rabin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar (47.7%) sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne kawai ke ƙasa da shekaru 20, kuma 14 ne kawai ke ƙarƙashin shekaru 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya yi wa maza da yawa illa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya yaɗu tsakanin ƙungiyoyi a cikin da kewaye da Hubei.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farkon kamuwa da cutar zuwa ganewar asali.
