Tushen dabbobi na kwayar cutar korona ta mutum
Juyin halitta da kuma daidaitawa sun jagoranci juyin halitta tsakanin coronaviruses da kuma masu masaukin su, ciki har da mutane, dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa nau'i biyu na kwayar cutar korona ta ɗan adam tana haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar mura.
Cutar SARS da cutar MERS sun nuna yadda cutar korona ta iya zama mai hadari da barazana ga rai.
Bayyanar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar kasar Sin a karshen shekarar 2019 ya sake haskakawa a kan coronaviruses, kuma mun yi mamakin yadda yake yaduwa da sauri amma tare da iyawar cutarwa idan aka kwatanta da dan uwansa SARS-CoV.
Kwayar cutar korona ta mutum wata cuta ce ta dabbobi, saboda haka fahimtar asalin kwayar cutar korona ta mutum daga dabbobi zai taimaka mana sosai.
Yawancin kwayar cutar korona ta mutum ta fito ne daga batsa inda ba ta haifar da cuta ba.
An kuma gano wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronaviruses na ɗan adam.
Gano dabbobi masu gida yana da tasiri kai tsaye wajen hana cututtuka a cikin mutane.
Binciken yadda kwayar cutar korona ke hulɗa da mai masaukin ta dabbobi ya kuma ba da muhimmiyar fahimta game da yadda kwayar cutar korona ta fara a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun ba da taƙaitaccen bayani game da kwayar cutar korona guda bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalin dabbobi da kuma canjin halittarsu.
