Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanar a ranar Laraba cewa barkewar cutar COVID-19, cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar korona mai nasaba da cutar mai saurin numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta, wadda aka fi sani da SARS-CoV-2, ta kai matakin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar nan " annobar" tana nuna yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda wasu cututtuka suke da tsanani ba, WHO ta yi kira ga gwamnatoci su dauki matakan da suka dace:
"Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin wannan annobar.
Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ya ce, "Idan kasashe suka gano kuma suka gudanar da gwajin mutane, da maganin su, da keɓe su, da bin diddigin yanayin su, da kuma tattara su don magance matsalar".
"Dukanmu muna matukar damuwa game da yaduwar cutar da kuma hadarin da ke damunmu da kuma rashin kulawa da ke nuna cewa akwai hadari".
A cewar Dokta Tom Friedden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar a Amirka, wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa kasancewa ba".
A cikin wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, "Ba a iya gano hanyar kowace kwayar cutar numfashi ba daga farkon bayyanarta zuwa ci gaba da yaduwar ta a duniya, sai dai mura".
Gebreussus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa: "Ba mu taɓa fuskantar annobar da wata kwayar cutar corona ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba, "Ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da za a iya shawo kanta ba".
An bayyana sabon yanayin a matsayin annoba bayan shawarar da WHO ta yanke a watan Janairu na ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a da ke haifar da damuwa ta duniya.
"Ainihin abin da za mu iya cewa shi ne, abubuwa za su ƙara muni", in ji Dokta Anthony Fauci, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Ciwo Mai Saurin Yaduwa a Amirka.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa a kalla mutane 126,000 ne suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya tun ranar Alhamis, kuma sama da mutane 4,600 ne suka mutu.
Cutar cutar korona 2019-20 cuta ce mai gudana ta cutar korona 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar korona 2 ke haifarwa, wadda ke da nasaba da cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin dokar ta baci ta duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an amince da ita a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu rahoton kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe da yankuna 210, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 97,000.
Kimanin mutane 364,000 sun warke.
An kiyasta cewa yawan mutuwar mutane a China ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari, yayin da a duniya ya kai 13.04% a Aljeriya da 0.08% a New Zealand.
Alamun da suka fi kowa sun haɗa da zazzabi, tari, da kuma rashin numfashi.
Ƙari ga haka, za a iya samun ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Lokaci tsakanin kamuwa da cutar da bayyanar cututtuka yawanci kwanaki biyar ne, amma yana iya wucewa daga kwana biyu zuwa kwana goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani rigakafi ko magani na musamman da aka sani game da cutar.
Magani na farko shi ne magani na tallafi da kuma na bayyanar cututtuka. Matakan rigakafi da aka ba da shawara sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki idan ka yi tari, nisantar mutane, sa ido, da kuma ware kai daga waɗanda ake zargin suna da cutar.
Hukumomi a dukan duniya suna amsa wannan barazanar ta wajen kafa takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, keɓewa, ƙuntatawa, da kuma hana haɗari a wuraren aiki da kuma rufe wuraren aiki.
Wannan annobar ta haifar da rikice-rikicen zamantakewa da tattalin arziki na duniya, an jinkirta ko soke wasanni, addini, siyasa, da al'adu, kuma an sami karancin kayayyaki da yawa wanda ya kara tsanantawa saboda tsoratar da sayayya.
Makarantu da jami'o'i sun rufe a kasa ko kuma a cikin gida a kasashe 193, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 cikin 100 na yawan daliban duniya.
Rashin gaskiya game da cutar ya bazu a intanet, kuma akwai wasu abubuwan da suka shafi tsoratar da baƙi da nuna bambanci ga Sinawa, da kuma wasu mutanen da suka fito daga Gabas da Kudu maso gabashin Asiya, da kuma wasu yankuna da ke da yawan kamuwa da cutar.
Sakamakon rage yawan tafiye-tafiye da rufe manyan masana'antu, an rage gurɓataccen iska da iskar carbon.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a birnin Wuhan (babban birnin lardin Hubei na kasar Sin) sun bayar da rahoton wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara bincike a farkon watan Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin cututtuka suna da nasaba da kasuwar cin abincin teku ta Wuhan, saboda haka ana ganin cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi.
Kwayar cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar an san ta da SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar cutar da aka gano wacce ke da alaƙa da coronaviruses a cikin bat, coronaviruses a cikin masu cin tururuwa, da SARS-CoV. An gano cewa mutumin da ya fara nuna alamun cutar ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma wannan mutumin ba shi da alaƙa da rukunin kasuwar da aka gano daga baya.
Daga cikin rukunin farkon shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku sun kasance da alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba da jaridar South China Morning Post ta wallafa ya nuna cewa wata mace mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, wacce ta fara kamuwa da cutar a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, na iya zama ta farko. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa duk da cewa an samu raguwar sabbin cututtuka a China, amma ba zato ba tsammani sun tashi a Italiya, Iran da Koriya ta Kudu, inda sabon adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a wajen kasar Sin ya zarce na sabon wadanda suka kamu da cutar a cikin gida a karon farko.
Akwai ƙarancin rahoton cututtuka, musamman ma a tsakanin waɗanda ke da ƙananan alamu.
A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, an samu rahotanni na ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta a tsakanin matasa, waɗanda shekarunsu suka kai 19 zuwa ƙasa da haka sun kai kashi 2.4% na masu kamuwa da cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa ana buƙatar kamuwa da kashi 60% na 'yan Burtaniya kafin a yi rigakafin garken da ya dace.
Lamuran sun nuna adadin mutanen da aka gwada wa COVID-19 kuma aka tabbatar da su a matsayin masu kamuwa da cutar bisa ga ka'idojin hukuma.
Ya zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawan jama'arta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa suna da manufofin hukuma na rashin gwada waɗanda ke da ƙananan alamun cutar, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka wallafa a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya gano cewa kusan kashi 86 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ba a gano su ba a kasar Sin, har zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, kuma wadannan cututtuka da ba a samu ba ne suka haifar da kashi 79 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga watan Maris ya nuna cewa adadin wadanda suka kamu a Italiya ya fi na waɗanda aka samu.
Ƙididdigar farko na R0 na COVID-19 ya kasance tsakanin 1.4 da 2.4.
Wani bincike da aka wallafa daga Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Amurka ya ce zai iya zama 5.7.
Yawancin mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna murmurewa.
Ga waɗanda ba su warke ba, lokaci daga ciwon ya yi muni zuwa mutuwa yana tsakanin kwanaki 6 zuwa 41, mafi yawan kwanaki 14 ne.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, COVID-19 ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane kusan 97,000.
Kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutuwar da aka yi a China tun daga ranar 5 ga Fabrairu sun kasance a cikin waɗanda suka haura shekaru 60, kuma kashi 75 cikin dari suna da cututtukan zuciya da ciwon sukari.
Adadin ainihin mutuwar COVID-19 na iya zama mafi girma, domin ba su haɗa da mutanen da suka mutu ba tare da an gwada su ba - misali, a gida, ko a gidan kula da tsofaffi, da sauransu.
Bayanai na Italiya sun nuna cewa adadin mutuwar da aka samu a lokacin annobar ya wuce adadin mutuwar COVID da aka samu a hukumance sau hudu zuwa biyar.
Mai magana da yawun Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar (CDC) a Amurka ta yarda cewa "mun san cewa [yawan mutuwar da aka sanar] ya nuna ƙarancin kimantawa", wata sanarwa da ke tallafawa rahotanni na almara da ke nuna rashin daidaito a cikin Amurka. Irin wannan rashin kimantawa yana faruwa a cikin annobar annoba; kamar annobar cutar sankarar naman alade ta H1N1 a shekarar 2009.
Mutuwa ta farko a waje da babban yankin China a ranar 1 ga Fabrairu a Philippines, kuma ta farko a wajen Asiya a Faransa a ranar 14 ga Fabrairu.
A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu mutuwar mutane fiye da goma sha biyu a kasashen waje na kasar Sin, a Iran, Koriya ta Kudu da kuma Italiya.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, sama da kasashe da yankuna arba'in ne suka bayar da rahoton mutuwar, a duk nahiyoyi ban da Antarctica. Ana amfani da matakai da yawa don tantance yawan mutuwar.
Waɗannan lambobin sun bambanta ta yanki da kuma lokaci, kuma suna shafar girman gwajin, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani da lokacin da ya ɗauka tun barkewar cutar, da halaye na yawan jama'a kamar shekaru, jinsi, da lafiyar jama'a. Matsayin mutuwa zuwa kamuwa da cuta yana nuna yawan mutuwar da aka raba da adadin waɗanda aka gano a cikin wani lokaci.
Bisa ga kididdigar Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, yawan mutuwar da raunin cutar a duniya ya kai 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) a ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020.
Adadin ya bambanta bisa ga yankin.
A China, kimantawar mutuwar cutar ta sauka daga kashi 17.3% (ga waɗanda ke da alamun cutar daga 1 zuwa 10 ga Janairu 2020) zuwa 0.7% (ga waɗanda ke da alamun cutar bayan 1 ga Fabrairu 2020). Sauran ma'auni sun nuna yawan mutuwar cutar (CFR), wanda ke nuna yawan waɗanda suka kamu da cutar da suka mutu, da kuma yawan mutuwar kamuwa da cuta (IFR), wanda ke nuna yawan waɗanda suka kamu da cutar (wanda aka tabbatar da cutar da wanda ba a tabbatar da cutar ba) da ke mutuwa daga cutar.
Waɗannan ƙididdigar ba su da lokaci kuma suna bin wani takamaiman rukunin jama'a daga kamuwa da cutar zuwa sanin makomar cutar.
Masana kimiyya da yawa sun yi ƙoƙarin yin lissafin waɗannan adadi don wasu mutane.
Cibiyar Nazarin Magunguna ta Jami'ar Oxford ta kiyasta cewa yawan mutuwar annobar a matsayin duka ya kai tsakanin kashi 0.1 zuwa 0.39 bisa ɗari.
Ƙididdigar da ta fi wannan girma ta yi daidai da sakamakon gwajin COVID-19 na farko da aka yi a Jamus, da kuma nazarin ƙididdiga da ke bincika tasirin gwajin a ƙididdigar yawan mutuwar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta tabbatar da cewa za a iya shawo kan annobar.
Ba a san lokacin da cutar za ta fi yaduwa ba kuma za ta iya bambanta da wuri.
Masage Bonney na Jami'ar Jihar Pennsylvania ya ce: "Yadda ake yawan samun cututtuka da ba a iya sarrafawa ba, sukan kai ƙarshensu kuma su fara raguwa sa'ad da cutar ba ta da masu masaukin kai.
Amma ba shi yiwuwa a yi wani zato mai kyau game da lokacin da hakan zai faru".
