Taiwan ta kara samar da abin rufe fuska kuma ta yi ta matse kayayyakin kiwon lafiya. Kwatancen da aka yi wa Birtaniya da Amurka ya nuna cewa rage (rage yaduwar cutar, ba dakatar da ita) da kuma hana (daidaita ci gaban cutar) suna fuskantar manyan kalubale.
Manufofin rage yawan cuta na iya rage yawan bukatar kiwon lafiya da kashi biyu cikin uku da kuma mutuwar mutane da rabi, amma har ila yau suna haifar da dubban dubban mutuwar mutane da kuma matsin lamba ga tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Ya kamata a ci gaba da hana kamuwa da cutar har sai cutar ta yaɗu a cikin mutane (ko kuma har sai an samu rigakafin cutar, idan hakan ta fara faruwa), amma ana iya kawar da kamuwa da cutar idan aka rage matakan.
Saurin hana annobar yana da tsada a fannin tattalin arziki da zamantakewa.
Babu takamaiman maganin rigakafin cutar da aka amince da shi don COVID-19, amma ana ci gaba da ƙoƙarin ci gaba, ciki har da gwajin magungunan da ake da su.
Shan magungunan sanyi da ba a rubuta wa likitanci ba, shan ruwa da hutawa na iya taimaka wajen rage ciwo.
Dangane da tsananin cutar, za a iya bukatar maganin oxygen, ruwan jini, da kuma taimakon numfashi.
Yin amfani da maganin hana ci zai iya sa sakamakon ya yi muni.
Ana gwada magungunan da yawa da aka amince da su a baya don magance wasu cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta don a yi amfani da su wajen maganin COVID-19.
Ƙungiyar Lafiya ta Duniya ta kuma ce wasu "magani na gargajiya da na gida" na iya rage alamun cutar SARS-CoV-19.
Ƙarfafa iya aiki da daidaita cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya don biyan bukatun marasa lafiya na COVID-19 an bayyana su ta WHO a matsayin manyan matakan magance barkewar cutar.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai da Ofishin Yankin WHO na Turai sun ba da jagororin asibitoci da ayyukan kiwon lafiya na farko don canja wurin albarkatu a matakai da yawa, gami da mayar da hankali kan gwajin COVID-19, kawar da zaɓin inda zai yiwu, warewa da ware COVID-19, haɓaka ƙarfin kulawa ta hanyar horar da ma'aikata da haɓaka yawan kayan numfashi da gadaje.
Akwai ra'ayoyi da yawa game da inda yanayin farko ya samo asali (wanda ake kira Mai haƙuri Zero).
An fara gano sabon cutar korona a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019 a birnin Wuhan, Hubei, a kasar Sin.
A cikin wata guda, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar korona a Hubei ya karu a hankali.
Wannan ya kasance mafi yawa game da kasuwar cin abincin teku ta Wuhan, wanda ke sayar da dabbobi masu rai, kuma daya daga cikin ka'idodin ya ce kwayar cutar ta fito ne daga ɗayan waɗannan nau'ikan dabbobi; ko kuma a wasu kalmomin, ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi. An lura da wani rukuni da ke fama da cutar huhu don dalilin da ba a sani ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba kuma an kula da shi a asibitin lardin Hubei ta hanyar Dr. Zhang Jixian, wanda ya sanar da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Jianghan Buhan a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Disamba, wasu likitoci a asibitin Wuhan na tsakiya sun gargadi abokan aikinsu game da "kwayar cutar korona mai kama da SARS".
An gargadi takwas daga cikin wadannan likitoci, ciki har da Li Wenliang, saboda yada jita-jita, kuma wani likita, Ai Wen, ya sha azaba daga shugabanninta don faɗakar da jama'a.
Daga baya kwamitin kiwon lafiya na birnin Wuhan ya fitar da sanarwa a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba kuma ya sanar da WHO.
An samu isassun rahotanni na kamuwa da cutar huhu da ba a san ko su waye ba ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, wanda ya sa suka fara bincike a farkon watan Janairu. A farkon lokacin barkewar cutar, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya ninka kusan sau biyu a kowace kwana bakwai da rabi.
A farkon da tsakiyar watan Janairun 2020, cutar ta bazu zuwa wasu lardunan kasar Sin, tare da taimakon tafiye-tafiye a lokacin Sabuwar Shekarar Sin da kuma Kun-Wuhan, cibiyar sufuri da kuma wurin da manyan layin dogo ke haɗuwa.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, kasar Sin ta bayar da rahoton kusan sabbin mutane 140 a rana guda, ciki har da mutane biyu a Beijing da daya a birnin Shenzhen.
Bayanai na hukuma da aka sanar daga baya sun nuna cewa mutane 6,174 sun riga sun nuna alamun cutar a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020. Ya zuwa ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta zarce China da Italiya a kan yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar a duniya. Ya zuwa ranar 9 ga Afrilu, 2020, an ba da rahoton sama da mutane miliyan 1.61 a duniya, tare da mutane sama da 97,000 da suka mutu, kuma sama da mutane 364,000 sun warke.
Kimanin ƙasashe 200 da yankuna sun sami aƙalla mutum ɗaya da ya kamu da cutar.
Saboda annobar a Turai, ƙasashe da yawa a yankin Schengen sun ƙuntata 'yancin motsi kuma sun kafa takunkumin kan iyakoki.
Amsoshin ƙasa sun haɗa da matakan hanawa, kamar su keɓewa (wanda aka fi sani da umarnin zama a gida, ko umarnin ɓoyewa, ko rufewa) da kuma dokar hana fita. Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Afrilu, kusan mutane miliyan 300, ko kusan kashi 90% na yawan jama'a, sun shiga cikin wani nau'in kulle-kulle a Amurka, sama da mutane miliyan 50 sun shiga cikin kulle-kulle a Philippines, kusan mutane miliyan 59 sun shiga cikin kulle-kulle a Afirka ta Kudu, kuma mutane biliyan 1.3 sun shiga cikin kulle-kulle a Indiya.
A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, mutane biliyan 1.7 a duniya sun shiga wani irin kulle-kullen, wanda ya kai biliyan 2.6 kwana biyu bayan haka - kusan kashi ɗaya bisa uku na yawan mutanen duniya.
An fara tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019 a Wuhan; wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ya nuna cewa an fara gano cutar ne a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba.
A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, Dr. Zhang Jixian ta lura da wasu cututtukan ciwon huhu da ba a san dalilin su ba, kuma asibitinta ya sanar da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Jianghan Wuhan a ranar 27 ga watan Disamba.
Gwajin farko na kwayoyin halittar marasa lafiya a ranar 27 ga Disamba, 2019 ya nuna cewa akwai kwayar cutar SARS.
Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na birnin Wuhan ya fitar da sanarwa a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba.
An sanar da WHO a ranar.
A yayin da ake samun irin wannan sanarwar, 'yan sanda sun gargadi likitoci a birnin Wuhan game da "rashin jin labarin" game da barkewar cutar.
A farko hukumar lafiya ta kasar Sin ta ce babu "bayyanannen shaida" na kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ƙarshen watan Janairu, gwamnatin China ta ƙaddamar da wani babban kamfen wanda daga baya Sakatare Janar na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin Xi Jinping ya kira "yaƙin jama'a" don hana yaduwar cutar.
A cikin abin da aka kwatanta da "mafi girman tsaftacewa a tarihin ɗan adam", an sanar da dokar hana zirga-zirga daga Wuhan a ranar 23 ga Janairu, wanda ya kai ga birane 15 a Hubei, wanda ya shafi kusan mutane miliyan 57.
An hana amfani da motoci masu zaman kansu a cikin birnin.
An soke bikin Sabuwar Shekarar Sin (Janairu 25) a wurare da dama.
Hukumomi sun kuma sanar da gina asibitin wucin gadi, asibitin Huishan, wanda aka kammala a cikin kwanaki 10.
An gina wani asibiti, asibitin Lichenshan, don kula da ƙarin marasa lafiya.
Baya ga sabbin asibitocin da aka kafa, kasar Sin ta kuma mayar da wasu wurare 14 a birnin Wuhan, kamar cibiyoyin taro da filayen wasa, asibitoci na wucin gadi. A ranar 26 ga watan Janairu, gwamnati ta dauki wasu matakai don shawo kan barkewar COVID-19, ciki har da bayar da sanarwar kiwon lafiya ga matafiya da kuma tsawaita hutun bikin bazara.
An kuma rufe jami'o'i da makarantu a duk fadin kasar.
An ɗauki matakai da yawa a Hong Kong da Macau, musamman game da makarantu da jami'o'i.
An yi amfani da hanyoyin yin aiki daga nesa a yankuna da dama na kasar Sin.
An kafa takunkumin hana tafiye-tafiye a cikin da kuma wajen Hobby.
An gyara hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a, kuma an rufe gidajen tarihi na ɗan lokaci a duk ƙasar Sin.
An kafa takunkumin hana zirga-zirgar jama'a a birane da dama, kuma an kiyasta cewa mutane miliyan 760 (fiye da rabin yawan jama'a) sun fuskanci wani nau'i na takunkumin fita. Bayan barkewar cutar ta zama ta duniya a watan Maris, hukumomin kasar Sin sun dauki tsauraran matakai don hana "kawo" cutar daga wasu ƙasashe.
Misali, Beijing ta sanya wa duk waɗanda suka dawo daga wasu ƙasashe keɓewar kai na kwanaki 14. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an sami mutum ɗaya da ya kamu da cutar a cikin ƙasar Sin a cikin kwanaki biyar da suka gabata, ta hanyar matafiyi da ya dawo Guangzhou daga Istanbul.
A ranar 24 ga Maris, 2020, Shugaban Majalisar Jiha ta Sin Li Ke Chiang ya bayyana raguwar yaduwar cututtukan da ke yaduwa a cikin gida da kuma sarrafa barkewar cutar a China.
An sassauta takunkumin tafiye-tafiye a Hubei a wannan ranar, ban da Wuhan, bayan watanni biyu da sanya dokar kulle. Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta sanar a ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020 cewa za a dakatar da shigar masu riƙe da biza ko izinin zama daga ranar 28 ga Maris, ba tare da takamaiman bayani game da lokacin da wannan manufar za ta ƙare ba.
Waɗanda suke son shiga ƙasar Sin za su nemi biza a ofishin jakadancin ƙasar Sin.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta bukaci kamfanoni da masana'antu su ci gaba da aiki a ranar 30 ga Maris, kuma ta ba da wasu kudade na karfafa gwiwa ga kamfanoni. Majalisar Jiha ta ayyana ranar makoki da za a fara da minti uku na shiru a ranar 4 ga Afrilu da karfe 10:00 na dare, daidai da bikin Qingming, duk da cewa gwamnatin tsakiya ta bukaci iyalai su nuna girmamawarsu ta yanar gizo don kiyaye nisantar jiki don gujewa sake barkewar COVID-19.
An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020.
Hukumar Lafiya ta kasa ta sanar da karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar a ranar 20 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda hakan ya danganta ne da taron da aka yi a Daegu na wani sabon addini da ake kira Shincheonji Jesus Church.
Ana zargin cewa mabiya Shincheonji da ke ziyartar Daegu daga Wuhan ne suka haddasa annobar.
Ya zuwa ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, mutane 1,261 ko kuma kusan kashi 13 cikin dari na masu bin coci 9,336 sun ba da rahoton alamun. Koriya ta Kudu ta sanar da matakan tsaro mafi girma a ranar 23 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, an bayar da rahoton fiye da mutane 2,000 da aka tabbatar da su a Koriya, inda suka haura zuwa 3,150 a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu.
An sanya dukkan sansanonin sojin Koriya ta Kudu a killace bayan gwajin da aka yi ya tabbatar da cewa sojoji uku sun kamu da cutar.
Lokaci na tashi daga jirgin ya shafi shi ma, kuma ya canza. Koriya ta Kudu ta aiwatar da shirin da aka ce shi ne mafi girma kuma mafi kyau a duniya don bincika mutane don cutar, ware duk wanda ke da cutar, da kuma gano waɗanda suka yi musu illa da kuma sanya su cikin keɓewa.
Hanyoyin gwajin sun hada da tilastawa sabbin masu shigowa kasashen duniya su bayar da rahoton alamun cutar ta wayar salula, a gwada mutane a cikin motocinsu da za a samu sakamakon gwajin a rana mai zuwa, da kuma kara yawan gwajin zuwa mutane 20,000 a rana.
Shirin na Koriya ta Kudu ya nuna nasara wajen shawo kan barkewar cutar duk da cewa ba a sanya dukkan biranen keɓewa ba. Da farko al'ummar Koriya ta Kudu sun rabu game da yadda Shugaba Moon Jae-in ya amsa rikicin.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun neman a cire Moon, suna zargin gwamnati da rashin kulawa da annobar, ko kuma suna yaba masa saboda yadda ya amsa.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, an sanar da cewa Koriya ta Kudu tana da mafi ƙarancin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a rana guda a cikin makonni huɗu.
A ranar 29 ga watan Maris, an sanar da cewa daga ranar 1 ga watan Afrilu, duk sabbin da suka shigo daga kasashen waje za a killace su na tsawon makonni biyu.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 1 ga Afrilu, Koriya ta Kudu ta samu buƙatun daga ƙasashe daban-daban 121 don taimakawa wajen gwajin cutar.
Iran ta bayar da rahoton farkon tabbataccen cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Qum, inda mutane biyu suka mutu daga baya a ranar, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Kiwon Lafiya.
Matakan farko da gwamnati ta sanar sun hada da soke kide kide da wake-wake da sauran al'adu da wasanni, sallar Juma'a, rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi da makarantu.
Iran ta ware tiriliyan biyar na Riyal don yaki da cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya bayyana a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020 cewa babu wani shiri na killace yankunan da cutar ta shafa, za a killace mutane ne kawai.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren rage tafiye-tafiye tsakanin birane a watan Maris, duk da cewa ana ci gaba da samun cunkoson zirga-zirga tsakanin birane kafin sabuwar shekara ta Farisa ta Nuwruz.
An ci gaba da bude wuraren ibadar Shia a Gumi har zuwa ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020. A watan Fabrairu, Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China.
A cikin zargin cewa Iran na rufe yaduwar cutar, sama da kasashe goma sun bi diddigin wadanda suka dawo daga Iran tun daga ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda ke nuna cewa yaduwar cutar na iya wuce adadin mutane 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, inda aka bayar da rahoton cewa mambobi 23 daga cikin 290 sun kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga watan Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta bukaci hukumomin gidan yari na Iran da su saki masu kare hakkin dan adam da aka tsare saboda adawa ta lumana ba tare da wani sharadi ba, da kuma 'yan fursunoni masu cancanta da za a sake su na wucin gadi.
Ta ce akwai babban hadarin yaduwar cutar a wuraren da aka rufe kamar gidajen yari, wanda kuma ba su da isasshen kulawar likita.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta sanar da mutuwar mutane 100 a rana daya, wanda shi ne mafi girma a kasar tun lokacin da annobar ta fara.
Aƙalla 'yan siyasa 12 da tsoffin jami'an gwamnati sun mutu sakamakon cutar a ranar 17 ga watan Maris.
A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, Iran na samun sabbin kamuwa da cutar 50 a kowace awa, da kuma mutuwar mutum daya a kowane minti goma saboda cutar korona.
A cewar wani jami'in WHO, adadin masu cutar a Iran zai iya ninka na baya sau biyar.
An kuma yi imanin cewa takunkumin Amurka akan Iran na iya shafar ikon kudi na kasar wajen magance barkewar cutar.
Hukumar kare hakkin dan adam ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki kan kasashen da cutar ta fi shafawa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da barkewar cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da gwajin SARS-CoV-2 na 'yan yawon bude ido na kasar Sin a Rome ya nuna cewa suna da cutar.
Lamarin ya fara ƙaruwa sosai, wanda ya sa gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da duk jiragen da ke zuwa da kuma fita daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
Daga baya an gano wasu marasa alaƙa da COVID-19, farawa da 16 da aka tabbatar a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, majalisar ministoci ta ba da sanarwar sabon doka don hana barkewar cutar, gami da keɓewa sama da mutane 50,000 daga gundumomi 11 daban-daban a arewacin Italiya.
Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte ya ce, "Ba za a yarda da kowa ya shiga ko ya fita daga yankunan da cutar ta bulla ba.
An riga an ba da umarnin dakatar da ayyukan kasuwanci da wasanni a waɗannan yankuna". A ranar 4 ga Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta ba da umarnin rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i a duk faɗin ƙasar, inda mutuwar mutane 100 a Italiya.
An shirya gudanar da dukkan manyan wasannin wasanni, ciki har da wasannin Premier League, a rufe har zuwa watan Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris, an dakatar da dukkan wasannin wasa gaba daya na akalla wata daya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya ba da umarnin dakatar da kusan duk ayyukan kasuwanci, ban da manyan kantuna da kantunan magani. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Kula da Magunguna, Mai ba da magani, Mai ba da taimako da kulawa mai zurfi (SIAARTI) ta buga shawarwarin ɗabi'a na likita game da hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su.
A ranar 19 ga watan Maris, Italiya ta zarce China a matsayin kasa da ta fi kowacce mace-mace da ke da nasaba da cutar korona a duniya bayan ta bayar da rahoton mutane 3,405 da suka mutu sakamakon annobar.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, Rasha ta aika da jiragen sama tara na soja dauke da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya zuwa Italiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 5 ga Afrilu, an samu mutane 128,948 da suka kamu da cutar, mutane 15,887 sun mutu, kuma mutane 21,815 sun kamu da cutar a Italiya, mafi yawansu a yankin Lombardy.
Rahoton CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da yawan tsofaffi da rashin iya gwada duk waɗanda ke da cutar a Italiya ya zuwa yanzu na iya taimakawa wajen ƙaruwar mutuwar.
Amsar Burtaniya ga cutar ta fara bayyana a matsayin mafi sassaucin ra'ayi a cikin ƙasashe da cutar ta shafa, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta ba da wani nau'i na nisantar zamantakewa ko matakan keɓewa ga 'yan ƙasa ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta fuskanci suka saboda rashin saurin da kuma tsananin amsawa ga damuwar da jama'a ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya ba da sanarwar da ke ba da shawarar kauce wa balaguro ko hulɗa da jama'a ba dole ba, yana ba da shawarar mutane suyi aiki daga gida kamar yadda zai yiwu kuma su guji wurare da yawa, kamar mashaya, gidajen cin abinci da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta rufe dukkan wuraren shakatawa kamar mashaya da wuraren motsa jiki da wuri-wuri, kuma ta yi alkawarin biyan kashi 80% na albashin ma'aikata har zuwa £2,500 a wata don rage rashin aikin yi a lokacin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da tsauraran matakan nisantar da jama'a, inda aka hana tarurruka sama da mutane biyu kuma aka hana tafiye-tafiye da aiki a waje da gida sai dai idan ya zama dole.
Ba kamar yadda aka saba ba, 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da wannan dokar ta hanyar ba da tarar da kuma tarwatsa taron jama'a.
An ba da umarnin rufe yawancin kamfanoni, ban da ayyukan kasuwanci "mahimmanci", ciki har da manyan kantuna, kantin magani, bankuna, shagunan kayan aiki, tashoshin mai, da kuma wuraren ajiye motoci.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an tabbatar da mutum na farko da aka sani da cutar COVID-19 a jihar Washington ta arewa maso yammacin Pacific a cikin wani mutum da ya dawo daga birnin Wuhan a ranar 15 ga watan Janairu.
An kafa rukunin aiki na fadar White House kan cutar korona a ranar 29 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta jama'a, kuma ta sanya takunkumi kan shigowar matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka (CDC), babbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka, ta sanar da cewa ta kirkiro gwajin kanta.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta jinkirta fara gwajin, ta rufe ainihin yaduwar cutar a lokacin.
Gwajin ya lalata gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga rukunin gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (ta hanyar ilimi, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa ƙarshen Fabrairu, da kuma takunkumin ƙa'idodin mutane don cancantar gwajin har zuwa farkon Maris (an buƙaci umarnin likita bayan haka).
A ranar 27 ga Fabrairu, jaridar Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, The Atlantic ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa: "Mutane da yawa da ke da alamun cutar kuma suna da umarnin likita suna jiran sa'o'i ko kwanaki don yin gwaji". Bayan an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Insley ya ayyana dokar ta baci, matakin da wasu jihohi suka bi.
Makarantu a birnin Seattle sun soke karatu a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, masana ilmin cututtuka na Jami'ar Imperial College London sun sanar da Amurka game da hasashen tasirin sabon kwayar cutar ta Corona a kasar.
A wannan ranar ne Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan dokar samar da karin tallafi don shirye-shiryen cutar korona da kuma mayar da martani, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 na kudade na gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don magance annobar.
Kamfanoni sun hana ma'aikata tafiya, sun soke taro, kuma sun bukaci ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke ayyuka da kuma wasannin motsa jiki. A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanar da hana tafiye-tafiye zuwa mafi yawan Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30, daga ranar 13 ga watan Maris.
Washegari, an ƙara takunkumi zuwa Birtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci, wanda ya ba da damar amfani da kudaden tarayya don magance matsalar.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, kamfanoni da dama sun rufe ko rage lokutan aiki a duk faɗin Amurka don a rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da annobar a jihohi 50 da kuma gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar ta COVID-19 10,700 a birnin New York, wanda ya fi adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan ya ce ya yi kama da nesa da jama'a ya yi nasara, inda kimantawa ta nuna raguwar ninki biyu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
Ya zuwa ranar 28 ga Maris, an tabbatar da mutane 32,308 a birnin New York, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu daga cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, an bayar da rahoton cewa akwai ƙarin tabbatar da cutar coronavirus a Amurka fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, gami da China da Italiya. Ya zuwa ranar 8 ga Afrilu, an tabbatar da mutane 400,335 a Amurka, kuma mutane 12,841 sun mutu.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaba Trump na Amurka ya yanke shawarar tsawaita dokokin nisantar juna har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
A wannan rana, jirgin USS Comfort, wani jirgin asibiti mai gado 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta yi rikodin mutuwar mutane 884 da cutar korona ta yi a cikin sa'o'i 24.
A jihar New York, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya zarce 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki fadar White House kan rage barazanar da kuma sarrafa yada labarai ta hanyar umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su daidaita bayanan jama'a da wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi cutar tare da ofishin mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence.
Gwamnatin Trump ba ta samu karbuwa ba saboda rikicin da ta haifar da rashin jituwa tsakanin jam'iyyun.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki yadda Amurka ke dogara da shigo da kayayyakin da ake bukata, ciki har da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya, daga China.
An yi amfani da nazarin yanayin tafiye-tafiye na iska don tsara fasalin yanayin yaduwar da kuma hasashensa, wanda aka buga a cikin mujallar Travel Medicine a tsakiyar watan Janairu na 2020.
Dangane da bayanan da aka samu daga Tarayyar Jirgin Sama ta Duniya na 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei sun fi yawan fasinjojin da suka fito daga Wuhan.
An kuma bayar da rahoton cewa Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne sune wuraren da matafiya daga Wuhan ke zuwa.
An bayar da rahoton cewa Bali ita ce mafi ƙarancin ƙarfi a cikin shahararrun wurare sama da 20 don yin shiri, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya suka fi ƙarfin. Ostiraliya ta fitar da tsarin gaggawa na gaggawa na sabon kwayar cutar ta COVID-19 a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ya ce ba a gano abubuwa da yawa game da cutar COVID-19 ba, kuma cewa Ostiraliya za ta ƙarfafa kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin amsa cutar.
A ranar 21 ga watan Maris, an ayyana dokar ta-baci ta kare lafiyar dan adam a Australia.
Saboda tasirin keɓewar jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, kasashe da dama sun shirya fitar da 'yan kasashensu da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, da farko ta hanyar jiragen da aka yi haya daga ƙasashensu, tare da samar da izini daga hukumomin China.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus, da Thailand suna cikin ƙasashe na farko da suka fara shirin kwashe 'yan ƙasarsu.
Pakistan ta sanar da cewa ba za ta fitar da 'yan kasarta daga China ba.
A ranar 7 ga Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko mutanen da aka kama, ban da 'yan Poland hudu, wani dan China, da kuma wani dan Indiya.
'Yan Poland, Sin da Indiya sun sauka daga jirgin a Poland, inda jirgin na Brazil ya tsaya kafin ya koma Brazil.
An ware 'yan Brazil da suka tafi Wuhan a wani sansanin soji da ke kusa da Brazil.
A wannan ranar, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (176 daga jirgin farko, 39 daga na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi haya) daga Wuhan zuwa sansanin sojojin Kanada na Trenton don ware su na tsawon makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a sansanin sojojin Kanada na Trenton.
Hukumomin Australiya sun kwashe mutane 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu zuwa wani wurin tsare da ake kira tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake amfani da shi a matsayin wurin keɓewa, inda suka zauna na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin saukar jiragen ruwa na New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, kuma an keɓe fasinjojinsa (ciki har da mutanen da suka fito daga Australia da Pacific) a sansanin sojan ruwa na Whangaparaoa a arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa da ke cikin jirgin Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, wani jirgin saman kamfanin jiragen sama na Afirka ta Kudu da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya ya dawo da 'yan kasar Afrika ta Kudu 112.
An yi wa 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu gwajin lafiya kafin su tashi, kuma an bar su da alamun cutar korona don rage haɗarin.
An mayar da 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka yi gwajin rashin lafiya.
Sakamakon gwajin ya tabbatar da cewa 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, ciki har da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji, waɗanda duk suka kasance, a matsayin matakan kariya, a karkashin sa ido da keɓewa a wurin shakatawa na Ranch na kwanaki 14, ba su da rauni.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta ruwaito cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad, Tobago, Misira, da Iran) sun aika da agaji zuwa China.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don aika da agaji zuwa yankunan da cutar ta addabi kasar Sin. Wani rukuni na hadin gwiwa a yankin Chicago ya samu nasarar aika da takunkumin N95 50,000 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu. Kungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da hadin gwiwar FedEx, ta aika da takunkumin 200,000 tare da sauran kayan kariya na mutum, ciki har da safofin hannu da tufafin ma'aikatan asibitoci, ta hanyar gadar jirgin sama, zuwa asibitin Wuhan Yunnan a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken rigakafi da kokarin magani, tare da kare "mutane masu hadarin gaske a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Interaction ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa birnin Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba Wuhan abin rufe fuska miliyan, Turkiyya ta aika kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan kiwon lafiya sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu ta kiwon lafiya miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita da suka hada da rigunan kariya 10,000, Amurka ta ba China tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita, kuma ta yi alkawarin bayar da tallafin kuɗi na dala miliyan 100 ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Bayan an daidaita yanayin a China, kasar tana aika da taimako ga ƙasashe daban-daban da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, Sin, Cuba, da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance barkewar cutar korona.
Dan kasuwa Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kuma riguna na kariya dubu 60,000, inda kungiyar tarayyar Afirka ta dauki nauyin rarraba su.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000 zuwa Panama, da abin rufe fuska 100,000, da kuma na'urorin numfashi guda biyar.
Ma kuma ta ba da gudummawar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a China.
Misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwajin cutar korona 58,000 da aka yi a China, wadanda suke da kashi 30 cikin 100 na daidaito, kuma a halin yanzu, Netherlands ta mayar da 600,000 na kayan rufe fuska da aka yi a China, wadanda suke da lahani.
Belgium ta mayar da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da aka yi zaton daga China ne, amma a zahiri daga Colombia ne.
A gefe guda, sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka sun yi maraba da karɓar taimakon na Sin da kyau. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya ƙaddamar da ayyukan tallafi na gaggawa ga ƙasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin China ke yi wajen sarrafa cutar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS tsakanin 2002 da 2004, inda ta zargi hukumomin China da rufewa wanda ya hana rigakafin da kuma hanawa, da kuma rikicin na yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta ba da "sabuntawa na yau da kullun don kauce wa firgita kafin hutun sabuwar shekara".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gudden Galleya ya lura cewa yayin da "ba shawarar WHO ba ce", amma "lambar da ke da matukar muhimmanci ga bin dokar hana yaduwar cutar a inda ta fi karkata", kuma ya bayyana ta a matsayin "marasa misaltuwa a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da yaduwar mutum zuwa mutum a wajen China, da kuma karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu kasashe, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ke da muhimmanci a duniya (PHEC), lamarin na shida na gaggawa a kiwon lafiyar jama'a tun lokacin da aka fara gudanar da wannan bincike a shekarar 2009.
Darakta Janar na WHO ya ce, an dauki annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a a duniya saboda "hadarin yaduwar ta a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu karancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da tsarin kiwon lafiya mai ƙarfi.
Da yake mayar da martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa a dauki matakan da ba dole ba ne su sabawa tafiye-tafiye da cinikayya ta kasa da kasa" kuma "Kungiyar Lafiya ta Duniya ba ta ba da shawarar rage kasuwanci da motsi ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 ga asusun dabarun da aka shirya a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi, inda ta nuna gaggawa ga tallafa wa ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da ke da cutar, ko da ta bayyana".
Tedros ya kuma yi jawabai inda ya bayyana cewa "an auna ƙarfinmu ne ta hanyar ƙarfin wanda ya fi rauni a cikinmu" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su "saka hannun jari a yau ko kuma su biya babbar farashin daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, a wani taron manema labarai, ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ruwaito cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da gabatar da "dukkanin tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a cikin martani".
Sakamakon haka, an kafa ƙungiyar kula da rikice-rikice ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita amsar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya gaba ɗaya, kuma zai ba da damar WHO "ta mai da hankali kan amsawar kiwon lafiya yayin da za a iya amfani da ƙwarewar sauran hukumomi don sanin tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki, da ci gaba na barkewar cutar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kafa tawagar hadin gwiwa ta WHO tare da China don kawo masana na duniya da na WHO a kan farfajiyar kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen gudanar da gida da kuma kimanta "taurin cutar da yaduwar ta" ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin kasa, da kuma gudanar da ziyarar filin don kimanta "tasirin ayyukan mayar da martani a larduna da birane, gami da birane da karkara". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa "ya kamata duniya ta yi ƙarin shiri don yiwuwar barkewar cutar coronavirus", tana mai cewa tun da farko an bayyana ta a matsayin annoba, amma ya kamata ƙasashe su kasance "a cikin matakin kulawa".
Yayin da ake amsa yaduwar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da tawagar hadin gwiwa a can don tantance halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a kara kimanta barazanar cutar coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mai matukar tsananin tsananin", wanda shine mafi girman matakin da take da shi na gargadi da kimanta hadari.
Mike Ryan, babban daraktan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin cewa "wannan gwaji ne na gaske ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: saboda haka dole ne mu kasance a shirye.
Wannan cuta na iya zuwa kuma ya kamata ku kasance a shirye don hakan", ya bukaci a dauki matakan da suka dace da za su iya taimakawa duniya ta guji "mafi muni".
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanan da ake da su yanzu ba su ba da hujjar cewa jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a su ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar na nufin "mun amince da cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana annobar korona a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO "tana da matukar damuwa game da matakan yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar, da kuma matakan rashin kulawa". WHO ta fuskanci sukar matuka game da abin da ake ganin rashin magance cutar, ciki har da jinkirin sanar da dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya, da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
Amsar ta hada da takardar neman murabus daga mukamin daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a kai, a ranar 6 ga watan Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, masana 'yancin bil'adama da dama a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun tabbatar da girmama haƙƙin kowane mutum yayin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin samun taimakon da zai ceci ransa kuma gwamnati ce ke da wannan hakkin.
Ƙungiyar ta nanata cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya bai kamata ya zama hujja don nuna bambanci ga wani rukuni ba.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, marasa gida, marasa gida, waɗanda ke rayuwa cikin mawuyacin yanayi, da waɗanda ke tsare, da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran rukunin da ba a bayyana su ba da suke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Ƙungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewa na rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar Tattalin Arziki ta kafa wani dandamali na samar da cikakken bayani a kan lokacin da ya dace game da martanin manufofin kasashe a duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga manufofin inganta tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya zuwa magance tasirin kulle-kulle da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, jigon dijital ya haɗa da kayan aikin bin diddigin manufofin ƙasa, kuma an yi niyyar taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen martani na duniya don magance cutar coronavirus.
Gwamnatin China ta fuskanci suka daga Amurka, Ministan ofishin Firayim Minista na Burtaniya Michael Goff, da Edward Bolsonaro dan shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro game da yadda suka magance annobar, wacce ta fara a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori wasu jami'an jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) a bangarori daban-daban saboda yadda suka bi da kokarin killace mutane a tsakiyar kasar, a wani bangare na nuna rashin jin dadin yadda hukumomin siyasa ke amsa annobar a wadannan yankuna.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan matakin ne don kare Sakatare Janar na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar su Zhao Lijian, sun ki amincewa da cewa annobar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan, suna goyon bayan ka'idodin makircin da Amurka ko Italiya ke da shi game da cutar COVID-19.
Gwamnatin Donald Trump ta Amurka ta kira kwayar cutar korona "kwayar cutar Sin" ko "kwayar Wuhan", tana mai cewa, China ta "sanya dokar hana fitar labarai da ta sa cutar ta kara muni, wanda yanzu ya zama annoba ta duniya", wanda wasu masu sukar suka soki saboda wariyar launin fata "kuma ya karkatar da [hankali] daga gazawar gwamnatinsa wajen shawo kan cutar".
Daily Beast ta samu wani sakon waya daga gwamnatin Amurka da ke nuna tsarin sadarwa daga majiyoyin da ke cikin majalisar tsaron kasa, tare da bayanin da ke cewa "dukkanin ya shafi kasar Sin.
An nemi mu yi kokarin yada wadannan sakonni ta kowace hanya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma fitowar talabijin. "Wasu kafofin watsa labarai kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin da China ke yi na aika da agaji ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa na daga cikin wani yunkurin da nake yi na yin tasiri a duniya.
Jami'in harkokin wajen Tarayyar Turai Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "wani bangare na siyasa na geopolitical wanda ya hada da gwagwarmayar tasiri ta hanyar yin amfani da karkatacciyar manufa da kuma siyasa".
Borrell ya kuma ce, "Sin tana tura saƙo da ƙarfi cewa, ba kamar Amurka ba, tana da alaƙa mai kyau da abin dogara".
China ta kuma bukaci Amurka ta dage takunkumin da ta kafa kan Syria da Venezuela da kuma Iran, yayin da ake cewa tana tura taimakon agaji ga kasashen biyu na karshe.
Takunkumin Amurka ya hana Jack Ma ba da gudummawar masks 100,000 ga Cuba a ranar 3 ga Afrilu.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amurka da tura taimakon da aka tura wa wasu kasashe zuwa kasarsu.
An kuma samu rigima game da abin rufe fuska a wasu ƙasashe, kamar Jamus, Austria, Switzerland, Czech Republic, da Italiya.
Bugu da ƙari, Turkiyya ta kwace ɗarurruwan na'urorin numfashi na roba da aka tura zuwa Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta soki rashin hadin kan Tarayyar Turai da Italiya da cutar korona ta shafa.
Mauritsu Massari, jakadan Italiya a Tarayyar Turai ya ce, "China ce ta amsa a matakin biyu kawai.
Hakika, wannan ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga haɗin kan Turai".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan tattaunawa ta waya da Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya sojojin Rasha su aika da jami'an agaji, motocin tsabtace jiki na musamman, da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta nakalto wani "babban jami'in siyasa" da ba a bayyana sunansa ba cewa kashi 80 cikin 100 na taimakon Rasha "ba shi da amfani ko kuma bai yi amfani da shi sosai ba ga Italiya".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da kaddamar da wani harin siyasa da diplomasiyya.
Shugaban Lombardy, Atilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya Luigi Di Maio sun musanta rahoton manema labarai kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Rasha ta kuma aika da jirgin ruwa mai dauke da kayan kiwon lafiya zuwa Amurka.
Mai magana da yawun Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ya ce "a wajen ba da taimako ga takwarorinsa na Amurka, [Butin] yana tunanin cewa lokacin da kamfanonin samar da kayan aikin likitanci na Amurka suka sake aiki, su ma za su iya mayar da alheri idan ya zama dole".
Za a gudanar da atisayen sojin NATO na "Gun 2020" a Jamus, Poland, da kuma ƙasashen Baltic, wanda shi ne mafi girma a cikin ayyukan soji da NATO za ta gudanar tun ƙarshen Yakin Cacar.
Babban sakataren kamfen din na kawar da makaman nukiliya Kate Hudson ya soki atisayen bindigogi na 2020 yana cewa: "A cikin rikicin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na yanzu, atisayen ba wai kawai suna sanya rayukan dakarun Amurka da na kasashen Turai da dama da ke shiga cikin hadari ba amma har da al'ummomin kasashen da za a gudanar da su". Gwamnatin Iran ta sha wahala sosai daga cutar, inda kusan 'yan majalisa ashirin da wasu tsoffin' yan siyasa goma sha biyar suka kamu da cutar.
Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wasika ga shugabannin duniya a ranar 14 ga Maris, 2020, yana neman taimako, yana mai cewa kasarsa tana fama da cutar saboda rashin samun damar zuwa kasuwannin duniya sakamakon takunkumin Amurka da aka sanya wa Iran. Barnar ta haifar da kira ga Amurka da ta amince da manufofin zamantakewar da suka zama ruwan dare a wasu ƙasashe masu arziki, ciki har da kiwon lafiya na kowa, kula da yara, izinin iyali da aka biya, da kuma matakan mafi girma na kudaden kiwon lafiya.
Masu sharhi na siyasa sun yi hasashen cewa hakan na iya shafar damar Donald Trump na sake zabarsa a zaben shugaban kasa na 2020. Dangantakar diflomasiyya tsakanin Japan da Koriya ta Kudu ta tabarbare saboda annobar.
