Cutar COVID-19 ta zama abin da ke nuna alaƙar ɗan adam da kuma hakkinmu ga wasu.
Tarihinmu bai taɓa ganin irin wannan ƙalubalen ba, amma mun san cewa amsa mafi kyau ta dogara ne da irin juyayi na duniya, haɗin kai da kuma gina al'umma, waɗanda sune abubuwan da suka fi dacewa a zuciyar wannan ma'aikata.
