A madadin haka, enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 mai dauke da amino acid carboxyl mai dauke da amino acid phenylelanine ya rabu da angiotensin 2 (aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-proline-phenylelanine) kuma ya canza shi zuwa angiotensin (1-7), (histidine-aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-proline-phenylelanine).
Enzyme mai canza Angiotensin 2 ya rabu zuwa wasu peptides da suka hada da [dis-arginine9] -bradricenin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da gerlin.
Hakanan enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 yana daidaita wucewar membrane na mai watsa amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19, kuma yana da rawa a cutar Hartnup.
Anzime mai canza Angiotensin 2, a matsayin furotin trans-membrane, shine babban hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na wasu coronaviruses, waɗanda suka haɗa da kwayar cutar ta NL63, SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS), da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da cutar COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗuwa da furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 tare da zangon enzymatic na enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 a farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cuta yana haifar da haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma yaduwar ƙwayoyin cuta da enzyme zuwa cikin kwayoyin da ke cikin ƙwayoyin.
Wannan aikin shigarwa yana buƙatar yin amfani da furotin S ta hanyar enzyme mai amfani da protease, mai masaukin baki, Serin2, wanda har yanzu ana hana shi a matsayin magani mai yiwuwa. Wannan ya sa wasu sun yi tunanin cewa rage matakan enzyme mai canza Angiotensin 2 a cikin ƙwayoyin zai iya taimakawa wajen tsayayya da kamuwa da cuta.
Ko yaya dai, ƙungiyoyi da yawa da kuma ƙungiyoyi masu sarrafa kansu suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da yin amfani da maganin da ake kira angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitors da kuma masu hana masu karɓa na angiotensin.
Wani bincike da kuma nazarin da aka yi a kan maganin da ake kira angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitors da aka wallafa a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya nuna cewa "a yi amfani da maganin da ake kira angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitors, an rage haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon huhu da kashi 34% idan aka kwatanta da na mutanen da aka yi amfani da su wajen yin maganin".
Bugu da ƙari, "yankan ciwon huhu ya ragu a tsakanin waɗanda aka yi wa maganin maganin na'urar hana yaduwar jini na angiotensin, waɗanda suka fi fuskantar ciwon huhu, musamman waɗanda suka yi bugun jini ko kuma rashin ƙarfi na zuciya.
Yin amfani da maganin hana enzyme mai canzawa zuwa angiotensin ya rage yawan mutuwar ciwon huhu, ko da yake sakamakon bai yi ƙarfi ba idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin ciwon huhu gaba ɗaya".
