Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na na'urar hannu da aka tsara musamman don taimakawa wajen bin diddigin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a cikin amsar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, wanda ke nufin gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ("masu kamuwa da cutar").
An tsara aikace-aikace da yawa ko kuma an gabatar da su tare da goyon bayan gwamnati a wasu yankuna da kuma yankuna.
An kafa tsarin aiki da yawa don tsara aikace-aikacen bin diddigin masu ɓarna.
Mutane da yawa sun nuna damuwa game da sirrin su, musamman game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin wurin da masu amfani da manhajoji suke.
Zaɓuɓɓuka da ba su da matsala wajen ɓoye sirri sun haɗa da yin amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rikodin kusanci da mai amfani daga wasu wayoyin salula.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar da cewa sun haɗa aikin da ke tallafawa waɗannan aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da Bluetooth, kai tsaye a cikin tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin tare da haɗin gwiwar Alipay ta fitar da wani manhaja da ke ba wa 'yan ƙasa damar duba ko sun yi hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19.
A yanzu haka, mutane suna amfani da shi a birane fiye da 200 a China, kuma a Singapore, mutane suna amfani da wani app da ake kira TraceTogether.
Kungiyar IT ta gida ce ta tsara wannan app, kuma ta fitar da shi a matsayin aikace-aikacen bude tushen da za a ba wa gwamnati. Macedonia ta Arewa ta ƙaddamar da "StopKorona", aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da Bluetooth don bin diddigin haɗarin haɗuwa da waɗanda ke da cutar da kuma ba da amsa mai sauri ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha tare da Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka tsara wannan app.
A ranar 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran amincewar Google Play da App Store daga Apple.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta ce ana ci gaba da inganta manhajar bin diddigin masu cutar, kuma za a iya rarraba ta cikin makonni. Ireland da Faransa suna shirin ƙaddamar da irin wannan manhajar, ("StopCovid").
Australia da New Zealand suna tunanin tsara aikace-aikace bisa TraceTogether da Singapore ta kaddamar, da kuma BlueTrees.Rasha na shirin gabatar da aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da yanayin yanayin ƙasa ga marasa lafiya da likitoci suka gano COVID-19 daga mazauna Moscow, wanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba sa barin gida.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a fannin aikin tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge, ya ambata wasu matsaloli na aiki da ke tattare da tsarin da ke kan aikace-aikace, ciki har da rashin inganci da rashin inganci idan amfani da aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙaramin ɓangaren jama'a.
Don magance damuwar yaduwar aikace-aikacen cutar coronavirus masu ɓatarwa ko cutarwa, Apple ya sanya takunkumi kan nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda za su iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da ke da alaƙa da cutar ta Corona zuwa shagon aikace-aikacen su; yana iyakance shi ga "hukuma" ko wasu ƙungiyoyi masu suna.
Google da Amazon sun kafa irin wannan takunkumi.
Masu kare sirrin sun nuna damuwa game da tasirin sa ido na jama'a da ake samu daga amfani da aikace-aikacen cutar korona, musamman idan tsarin sa ido da aka tsara don magance annobar korona zai tafi da zarar barazanar ta wuce.
Kungiyar Amnesty International da fiye da wasu kungiyoyi 100 sun fitar da wata sanarwa da ke kira ga takaita irin wannan sa ido.
Ƙungiyoyin sun kuma bayyana sharudda takwas ga ayyukan gwamnati:
Ya kamata a yi sa ido "daidai, dole, kuma daidai".
Ya kamata a haɗa da ƙarin lokaci na sa ido da kuma sa ido a kan lokacin da za a dakatar da su;
Ya kamata a ƙuntata amfani da bayanai don dalilai da suka shafi COVID-19.
Tsaron bayanai da sirrin su ya kamata a kiyaye kuma a tabbatar da hakan bisa hujjoji;
Ya kamata sa ido na dijital ya guji ƙara nuna bambanci da kuma warewa;
Ya kamata a ƙayyade ko wane irin rabawa ne na bayanai da wasu a cikin doka;
Ya kamata a samar da abubuwan karewa daga cin zarafi da kuma kare hakkin 'yan kasa wajen magance cin zarafi;
Ana buƙatar "haɗin kai" daga duk "masu ruwa da tsaki" da suka shafi, ciki har da masana kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ƙungiyoyin da ke kan iyaka. Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Jamus da kuma Reporters Without Borders (RSF) sun fitar da jerin bita.
Shirin Google/Apple da aka gabatar yana nufin magance matsalar sa ido ta hanyar cire tsarin bin diddigin na'urori daga tsarin aiki da zarar an daina bukatarsu.
Wasu ƙasashe sun yi amfani da hanyar sa ido ta hanyar hanyar sadarwa maimakon amfani da manhajoji, wanda hakan ya kawar da bukatar saukar da manhajoji kuma ya ba da damar kaucewa sa ido.
A Isra'ila, jami'ai sun amince da bin hanyar sadarwa.
Amma hanyoyin sadarwa da ke da damar shiga bayanan farko na wurin da ake zama suna da matsala mai girma game da tsare sirri.
Duk da haka, ba dukan tsarin da ke da maɓallin keɓaɓɓun suna bukatar samun damar yin amfani da bayanan wurin da mutum yake ba; an kafa wasu tsarin tsare sirri da ke amfani da maɓallin keɓaɓɓun don sadarwa kawai (duba sashe na gaba a ƙasa).
A Koriya ta Kudu, jami'ai sun yi amfani da tsarin da ba na aikace-aikace ba don bin diddigin masu yin ɓarna.
Maimakon amfani da wata manhaja, tsarin yana tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban-daban, ciki har da bayanan sa ido na na'urorin hannu da bayanan ma'amalar katin, kuma yana haɗa wannan bayanan don aika sanarwar saƙon rubutu ga mutanen da ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Baya ga amfani da wannan bayanin don faɗakar da masu ɓoye ɓoye, gwamnati ta kuma ba da damar samun bayanan wurin a fili, saboda canje-canje masu yawa a cikin dokokin tsare sirri bayan barkewar cutar coronavirus a wannan ƙasar.
Ana samun wannan bayanin a fili ta hanyar aikace-aikace da kuma shafukan intanet. Ƙasashe, har da Jamus, sun yi la'akari da yin amfani da tsarin da aka kafa da kuma tsare sirri.
A ranar 6 ga Afrilu, 2020, ba a fitar da cikakken bayani game da wannan ba.
Masu amfani da keɓaɓɓun bayanan sirri suna bin ingantaccen tsari mai nasara wanda ke da goyon bayan ingantaccen wallafe-wallafen bincike wanda ya fara aƙalla 2013. A ranar 7 ga Afrilu, 2020, fiye da gungun masana da dama sun yi aiki don samar da hanyoyin da suka dace da sirri, kamar Bluetooth mai ƙarancin ƙarfi (BLE) don yin rikodin kusanci da mai amfani daga wasu wayoyin hannu.
Duk da haka, BEP-BT ya kasance ƙoƙari ne na daidaitawa wanda ya ƙunshi duka hanyoyin da aka mayar da hankali da kuma rarraba, ba yarjejeniya ba. Hanyoyin da aka rarraba sun haɗa da tsarin kulawa da keɓaɓɓen tsarin (DP-PBT/DP-3T), lambobin tuntuɓar wucin gadi (TCN, wanda aka sani da lambar taron lamba, CEN), ladabi mai mahimmanci, da kuma bin diddigin masu amfani da na'urorin hannu (PECT) da sauransu.
A cikin waɗannan ƙa'idodin, bayanan sirri ba sa barin na'urar, kuma duk abubuwan da suka dace suna faruwa a na'urar.
Ƙungiyar tsare sirri a MIT Media Lab tana aiki kan ci gaba da SafePaths, wani dandamali don amfani da fasahohin tsare sirri lokacin tattara bayanai na wuri ko kuma hanyar haɗuwa da amfani da su don bin hanyar yaduwar COVID-19.
Ya dogara ne da bincike da aka samu daga rahoton "Maganar Aikace-aikacen: Kula da Sirrin Sirri a cikin Cutar", wanda aka fitar a watan Maris na 2020. Tsarin SafeTrace na Enigma MPC, wani kamfanin haɓaka fasahar tsare sirri wanda kuma ya samo asali a MIT Media Lab, wani irin wannan ƙoƙari ne.
SafeTrace tana amfani da fasahohin tsaro na na'ura don ba masu amfani damar raba bayanai na wuri da kuma lafiyar mai amfani da sauran masu gudanarwa ba tare da lalata sirrin bayanai ba.
A ranar 5 ga Afrilu, 2020, an kafa Ƙungiyar Kula da Lambar Sadarwa ta Duniya ta ƙungiyoyi waɗanda ke da sha'awar abin da ya kasance kusan irin wannan tsarin aiki da kuma hanyoyin sadarwa masu rikitarwa, da nufin rage rikicewa da kuma ba da damar musayar duniya tsakanin aikace-aikacen sa ido da faɗakarwa, babban fasalin samun yaduwar amfani.
A ranar 9 ga Afrilu, 2020, gwamnatin Singapore ta sanar da cewa ta sanya yarjejeniyar BlueTress, wacce aikace-aikacen gwamnati ke amfani da ita, ta zama mai buɗewa.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple, kamfanonin da ke sarrafa tsarin aiki na wayoyin hannu na Android da iOS, sun sanar da wani shiri na bin diddigin masu shiga tsakani; suna mai cewa za su kiyaye sirrin ta hanyar dogaro da haɗin Bluetooth mai ƙarancin ƙarfi da ɓoye sirrin sirri.
